skills.name: CORRUPTION
desc: • Deal one hit of physical, magic and true damage to all enemies.
• Transform Invincibility on each enemy into Perfect Corruption for 2 turns.
• Inflict Perfect Disable on all enemies for 2 turns.

skills.name: SECOND COMING
desc: • Remove All Negative Effects, including Silver effects, from all allies.
• 35% Chance to grant an Extra Turn to each ally.

skills.name: CALAMITY
desc: • Grant Immunity to Permadeath, Perfect Death, Block Beneficial Effects, and Perfect Corruption to all allies.
• Deal Additional True Damage to a random enemy equal to 500% of their MAX HP and Heal all allies to full HP when an ally dies.

• Remove All Beneficial Effects, including Golden effects, from all enemies, inflict Punishment and Perfect Death on all enemies for the duration of battle and Revive with full HP and a Perfect Titan Shield upon death..
